olor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute h-[1.2rem] w-[1.2rem] rotate-90 scale-0 transition-all dark:rotate-0 dark:scale-100 text-blue-400\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"inline-flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-border bg-white dark:bg-black text-foreground transition-all focus:outline-none\" aria-label=\"Toggle Navigation Menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><section class=\"py-12 md:py-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-4\"><span class=\"inline-block bg-muted text-primary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase px-2.5 py-1 rounded-md\">The Knowledge Base</span><h1 class=\"font-display text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary sm:text-5xl\">Compliance resources designed for founders.</h1><p class=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed\">Skip the legal jargon. Access practical guides, templates, and regulatory timelines to keep your startup pristine.</p></section><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2 mb-10 pb-4 border-b border-border/60\"><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer bg-primary text-primary-foreground shadow-sm\">All</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer bg-muted text-muted-foreground hover:bg-muted/80\">CAC &amp; Incorporation</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer bg-muted text-muted-foreground hover:bg-muted/80\">Tax &amp; FIRS</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer bg-muted text-muted-foreground hover:bg-muted/80\">Data Privacy</button><button class=\"px-4 py-2 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full transition-all cursor-pointer bg-muted text-muted-foreground hover:bg-muted/80\">General</button></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 mb-16\"><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">CAC &amp; Incorporation</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">CAC Annual Returns: What Happens If You Don&#x27;t File</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Every year, early-stage startups drop the ball on statutory updates. Here is exactly how missing your window triggers penalties and structure loss.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/cac-annual-returns-what-happens-if-you-dont-file\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">Data Privacy</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">NDPA Basics: What Every Tech Startup Needs to Know</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">A practical guide to the Nigeria Data Protection Act. Learn whether your startup is a major data controller and how to avoid heavy regulatory audits.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/ndpa-basics-startup-compliance\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">CAC &amp; Incorporation</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent bg-accent/10 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg> Guide + PDF</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">Post-Incorporation Checklist for Nigerian Startups</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">You&#x27;ve got your RC number—now what? Access the step-by-step statutory checklist including tax registration timelines, bank setup, and local permits.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium bg-red-50 text-red-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-red-100 dark:bg-red-950/20 dark:text-red-400 dark:border-red-900/30\">PDF</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/post-incorporation-checklist-nigeria\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">General</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">Compliance Consultant vs. Lawyer: Who Do You Actually Need?</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Stop overpaying for routine corporate filings. Learn when to hire a specialized corporate law firm and when a compliance consultancy is faster and cheaper.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/compliance-consultant-vs-lawyer-startup-guide\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">Tax &amp; FIRS</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">Startup Tax Registration: Navigating FIRS &amp; State Tax Boards</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">A complete walkthrough of registering for TIN, understanding VAT obligations, and setting up corporate tax structures without legal headaches.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/tax-registration-firs-scucl-requirements\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">CAC &amp; Incorporation</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-600 bg-emerald-50 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:text-emerald-400 dark:bg-emerald-950/30\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-download h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 15V3\"></path><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><path d=\"m7 10 5 5 5-5\"></path></svg> Download</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">The Nigerian Startup Compliance Deadline Calendar</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Never miss a statutory deadline again. Download this interactive calendar package complete with PDF tracker and ICS calendar imports for Google/Outlook.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium bg-red-50 text-red-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-red-100 dark:bg-red-950/20 dark:text-red-400 dark:border-red-900/30\">PDF</span><span class=\"text-[10px] font-medium bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-950/20 dark:text-blue-400 dark:border-blue-900/30 inline-flex items-center gap-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-calendar h-2 w-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M8 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M16 2v4\"></path><rect width=\"18\" height=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\" rx=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M3 10h18\"></path></svg> ICS</span></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/nigerian-startup-compliance-deadline-calendar\">Get Download<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">General</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">Who Regulates What: A Founder&#x27;s Guide to Nigerian Regulatory Bodies</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Demystifying the alphabet soup of Nigerian regulatory agencies. Learn exactly when your startup needs to deal with CBN, SEC, NITDA, FCCPC, or NAFDAC.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/who-regulates-what-founders-guide\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div class=\"group border border-border bg-card-surface p-6 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between hover:shadow-md transition-all hover:border-primary/20\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted-foreground\">General</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary bg-primary/5 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-white/10\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-open h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 7v14\"></path><path d=\"M3 18a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h5a4 4 0 0 1 4 4 4 4 0 0 1 4-4h5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v13a1 1 0 0 1-1 1h-6a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-3-3z\"></path></svg> Guide</span></div><h3 class=\"font-display text-lg font-bold text-primary group-hover:text-accent transition-colors line-clamp-2\">5 Compliance Mistakes That Get Nigerian Startups Fined</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed line-clamp-3\">Real-world cautionary tales of early-stage compliance failures in Nigeria. Avoid the quiet administrative errors that drain startup runways.</p></div><div class=\"pt-6 mt-6 border-t border-border/40 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"></div><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-accent group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform\" href=\"/resources/5-compliance-mistakes-nigerian-startups-fined\">Read Guide<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right h-3 w-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div></div><section class=\"bg-muted/40 border border-border p-8 rounded-3xl max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-6 mb-16\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-xl font-bold text-primary\">Get statutory updates before they pass.</h2><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-lg mx-auto leading-relaxed\">We track the FIRS, CAC, and NDPC so you don&#x27;t have to. Subscribe to get regulatory reminders directly in your inbox.</p></div><form class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 max-w-md mx-auto\"><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Enter your email\" required=\"\" class=\"flex-grow bg-white border border-border text-sm px-4 py-2.5 rounded-xl outline-none focus:border-accent transition-colors dark:bg-black/20\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-bold text-xs px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:brightness-105 transition-all inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg> Subscribe</button></form></section></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40 mt-auto\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-[1.4fr_1fr_1fr_1fr]\"><div class=\"max-w-sm space-y-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield-check h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"font-display text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-primary\">The Startup Desk</span></a><p class=\"text-xs leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground\">Compliance handled from your first CAC filing to your first funding round. A compliance consultancy for early-stage Nigerian startups, not a law firm.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary\">Explore</p><ul class=\"mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs font-semibold\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/services\">Services</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/resources\">Resources Hub</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary\">Legal &amp; Compliance</p><ul class=\"mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs font-semibold\"><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/terms\">Terms of Service</a></li><li><a class=\"text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\" href=\"/disclosures\">Regulatory Disclosures</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-primary\">Get in touch</p><ul class=\"mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs font-semibold\"><li><a href=\"mailto:the.start.up.desk1@gmail.com\" class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-primary\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-wid